ope it will be translated into more languages so that many WordPress users can use it conveniently.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\'WooCommerce\' ì íêµ­ì´ ë²ì­ì ëª¨ë ë§ì³¤ìµëë¤.<br />ì¢ì íë¬ê·¸ì¸ì ê°ë°í´ì£¼ì´ì ê³ ë§ë¤ë ì¸ì¬ë¥¼ ì íê³  ì¶ìµëë¤.<br />ê·¸ë¦¬ê³  \'WooCommerce\' íë¬ê·¸ì¸ì´ ë³´ë¤ ë¤ìí ì¸ì´ë¡ ë²ì­ëì´ ë§ì ìëíë ì¤ ì¬ì©ìë¤ì´ í¸ë¦¬íê² ì¬ì©í  ì ìê¸°ë¥¼ ë°ëëë¤.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Woocommerce is the worst ever needed tool</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fcipolla/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6e163b94036e62c6f394732bccf78d41?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6e163b94036e62c6f394732bccf78d41?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fcipolla/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">fcipolla</a> op <span class=\"review-date\">juni 17, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is hard to understand for whatreaso Woocommerce is so  lack, blemish, so unmanageble to deal off. I hope  that another better tool could poor constructionreplace it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Don&#039;t bother with this plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sutailia/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/87c270fdbc635d102ff349701a2cddf5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/87c270fdbc635d102ff349701a2cddf5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sutailia/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sutailia</a> op <span class=\"review-date\">juni 17, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'ve used this plugin on several sites.  The plugin is frequently glitchy, they don\'t update code to keep up with other major themes/plugins, and their support is completely non existent.  And they takes weeks to respond to support tickets just to tell you to do things you already did and if that doesn\'t work to go to the forums, which was already done.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>They will also nickel and dime you with every single tiny feature.  Seriously, don\'t waste your time and find